      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;David, a brilliant architect haunted by his wife's brutal, unsolved murder, returns to New York City with a singular, burning purpose: vengeance. His target? The city's corrupt elite, intricately tied to the multi-million dollar redevelopment project that is his last chance at redemption. But this project is a Trojan horse, a meticulously crafted blueprint for their downfall.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Consumed by grief and a desperate need for release, David's life unravels into a dangerous web of forbidden desires. His intimate encounters become raw, explicit outlets for his pain, pushing boundaries with women who find their own unique pleasure in his uninhibited passion. From Sarah, the wronged teacher seeking genuine connection, to Isabella, the dominant neighbor with a dangerous agenda; from Chloe, the ambitious colleague, to Eleanor, the powerful boss who demands absolute surrender; and even Lena, the free-spirited outsider, and Cassandra, the sheltered heiress awakening to a world of sensation—each woman is a piece of David's complex game, a source of both exquisite pleasure and perilous information.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;As the lines between love, lust, and lethal ambition blur, David's actions spark a "contagion of desire" that threatens to expose his meticulously guarded secrets. Can he dismantle the corrupt empire that stole his past without losing his soul, his daughter, and his very life in the process? Or will his desperate quest for justice consume him in a blaze of forbidden passion?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
