      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bri Wilkinson is an ostensibly cisgender bisexual guy who has a beautiful partner, Stephanie Miller. Their wedding date is fast approaching, and Bri knows that their big day will have to be the most special, magical, and memorable one of their lives, especially considering Bri has been having severe depression and anxiety leading up to the wedding. Little does he know, Stephanie plans to make it magical and memorable in more ways than one, and plans to help "him" discover who "he" truly is.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;(closeted trans woman experiences severe dysphoria over having to be in a masculine role at wedding, her life partner helps her figure out who she is and how she will live her new life using powerful magic)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
